  • https://docs.python.org/3.10/library/turtle.html
import cpython/turtle

title "Nim Turtle"
shape "turtle"
shapesize 2, 2, 8
color "green", "yellow"
speed "fast"
beginFill()

while true:
  forward 200
  left 170
  if position() < (1.0, 1.0):
    break

endFill()
mainLoop()
